{"id":18042,"date":"2022-12-31T04:27:06","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:27:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/cong-nghe-vat-lieu-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua-volvo.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:27:06","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:27:06","slug":"cong-nghe-vat-lieu-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua-volvo","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/cong-nghe-vat-lieu-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua-volvo\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u \u2013 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft sang tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Volvo"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>H\u00e3ng xe Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 an to\u00e0n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1edd c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn nh\u01b0 th\u00e9p boron v\u00e0 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">So v\u1edbi th\u00e9p c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c, th\u00e9p bo m\u1ea1nh g\u1ea5p 4 l\u1ea7n, gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i trong xe khi x\u1ea3y ra tai n\u1ea1n.  Boron \u2013 c\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i th\u00e9p si\u00eau c\u1ee9ng \u2013 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u201cb\u1ea3o b\u1ed1i\u201d c\u1ee7a Volvo trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc xe an to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac th\u00e2n xe Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Volvo v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nhau.  M\u00e0u xanh d\u1ecbu l\u00e0 nh\u00f4m, c\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf, t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc l\u1ed3ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i trong xe.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua.jpg\" title=\"cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua-600x424.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac th\u00e2n xe Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Volvo v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nhau.  M\u00e0u xanh n\u00ean l\u00e0 nh\u00f4m m\u1ec1m, c\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf, t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh \u201cchi\u1ebfc l\u1ed3ng\u201d b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i trong xe.  \u1ea2nh: Volvo.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Boron l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00e1 kim c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n k\u00e9o cao nh\u1ea5t trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u.  Do \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta tr\u1ed9n boron v\u00e0o th\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9.  Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 boron ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn 1% v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng l\u00ean g\u1ea5p 4 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i th\u00e9p gia c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng.  N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p su\u1ea5t l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 1400 N\/mm2 (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kho\u1ea3ng 203.000 psi).<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Kho\u1ea3ng gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 2000, lo\u1ea1i th\u00e9p n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t xe h\u01a1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.  V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Porsche Cayenne 2002, Boxster 2003, Merceddes E-class 2003, Volvo v\u1ed1n coi an to\u00e0n l\u00e0 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o xe.  Khung c\u1ee7a XC90 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi 40% th\u00e9p boron, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c trong ng\u00e0nh.  N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 khi va ch\u1ea1m tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c b\u00ean h\u00f4ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng khi xe b\u1ecb l\u1ed9n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Volvo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt h\u00e3ng xe \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ra t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng xe b\u1ecb l\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_801_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m an to\u00e0n xe Volvo\" title=\"1672429204_801_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_801_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_801_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_801_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua.jpg 750w\"><\/p>\n<p>Th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m an to\u00e0n xe Volvo<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m va ch\u1ea1m tr\u00ean XC90.  Video: Truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh k\u1eb9t xe.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Volvo c\u0169ng khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o c\u00e1c gara r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1eaft th\u00e9p boron b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1y c\u1eaft ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e8n plasma l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p.  Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi 9 chi\u1ebfc k\u00ecm c\u1eaft chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1edfi m\u00e1y b\u1ebb th\u1ee7y l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c (l\u00ean t\u1edbi 1112 kN \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u00e9p bo c\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t).<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh th\u00e9p, m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Volvo l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t m\u1ec1m: da b\u1ecdc.  T\u1eeb n\u0103m 2021, h\u00e3ng xe Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay th\u1ebf to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u da tr\u00ean xe b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u m\u1edbi c\u00f3 t\u00ean \u201cNordico\u201d t\u1ef1 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u1edbi tr\u00ean Volvo C40.  \u1ea2nh: Volvo.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_744_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua.jpg\" title=\"1672429204_744_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_744_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_744_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_744_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u1edbi tr\u00ean Volvo C40.  \u1ea2nh: Volvo.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c thay v\u00ec da \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfc crossover \u0111i\u1ec7n C40 c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng.  Volvo cho bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1eeb chai PET, n\u00fat chai t\u00e1i ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u sinh h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c khu r\u1eebng \u1edf Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea7n Lan.  V\u1eadt li\u1ec7u m\u1edbi n\u00e0y s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe Volvo.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ngo\u00e0i Nordico, Volvo cho bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t pha tr\u1ed9n len.  Volvo \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t k\u00eau g\u1ecdi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng len \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn v\u00ec l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.  Ngo\u00e0i ra, Volvo \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u nhi\u1ec1u v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa m\u00e0 h\u00e3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho gh\u1ebf ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0 b\u1ecdc n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf ho\u1eb7c m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng da.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">M\u1ef9 \u2013 Anh<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n cho \u00d4 t\u00f4 c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2022\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_224_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua.jpg\" title=\"1672429204_224_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_224_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua-240x300.jpg 240w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_224_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672429204_224_cong-nghe-vat-lieu-e28093-bi-quyet-sang-trong-cua.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">L\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n trao gi\u1ea3i Xe c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2022.  &gt;&gt; \u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd tham d\u1ef1<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u00e3ng xe Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 an to\u00e0n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1edd c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn nh\u01b0 th\u00e9p boron v\u00e0 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u1edbi. So v\u1edbi th\u00e9p c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c, th\u00e9p bo m\u1ea1nh g\u1ea5p 4 l\u1ea7n, gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i trong xe khi x\u1ea3y ra [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":16994,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18042"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18042"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18042\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16994"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=18042"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=18042"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=18042"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}